sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant R as VllmPDRouter
    participant P as Prefill实例
    participant D as Decode实例

    rect rgb(230,245,255)
    Note over C,D: ===== 初始化 =====
    R->>P: GET /health (循环等待200 OK)
    P-->>R: 200 OK
    R->>D: GET /health (循环等待200 OK)
    D-->>R: 200 OK
    R->>P: GET /query (获取engine_id)
    P-->>R: {dp_rank: {engine_id}}
    Note over P: 注册KV内存到TransferEngine
    Note over D: 注册KV内存到TransferEngine
    Note over R: 启动后台健康检查(每30-60s)
    end

    rect rgb(255,250,230)
    Note over C,D: ===== 后台健康检查 =====
    loop 每 check_interval_secs
        R->>P: GET /health
        P-->>R: 200 OK / 超时
        R->>D: GET /health
        D-->>R: 200 OK / 超时
        Note over R: 连续失败>=3 -> 标记unhealthy
        Note over R: 连续成功>=2 -> 恢复healthy
    end
    end

    rect rgb(245,240,255)
    Note over C,D: ===== 请求处理 =====

    C->>R: POST /v1/chat/completions

    Note over R: 同时选择P和D, 过滤不健康节点

    R->>P: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(max_tokens=1, do_remote_decode:true)
    Note over P: 执行Prefill, 生成KV Cache
    P-->>R: 200 {kv_transfer_params: remote_block_ids, remote_host, remote_port}

    Note over R: 附加kv_transfer_params转发给D

    R->>D: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(原始max_tokens, do_remote_prefill:true)

    D->>P: P2P RDMA: 拉取KV Cache (NPU-to-NPU直传)
    P-->>D: 传输完成
    Note over P: 释放KV Cache blocks

    Note over D: 跳过prefill, 开始decode

    loop 逐token流式输出
        D-->>R: Stream chunk
        R-->>C: SSE data
    end
    D-->>R: [DONE]
    R-->>C: [DONE]
    end
